text.section:
Any course offered by the Commission under subsection (c) of this section:
shall be offered free of charge or fee;
may not be more than 2 hours in duration;
shall be conducted or offered at least once each week in all geographic areas of the State;
shall be available after regular business hours;
shall be open to each individual required by law to complete the firearms safety training course, within 2 weeks after request of the individual;
shall only require attendance throughout the duration of the course in order to complete the course successfully; and
may not require any skills or knowledge testing in the use of a regulated firearm in order to complete the course successfully.
